Seseorang telah menemaniku.

00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:36.320
Akshay!

00:00:36.840 --> 00:00:38.960
Akshay.. Akshay, aku minta maaf.

00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:42.080
“Dari hutan rambut kusut-Nya
mengalir air suci yang mensucikan.”

